    <h1>About Disaster Null</h1>
    <p>At Disaster Null, our mission is simple: connect people in need with volunteers and responders in real time. Whether it's a flood, fire, or other emergency, we make sure help is never far away.</p>

    <div class="report-card">
      <h3>🌍 Our Mission</h3>
      <p>We aim to empower communities by providing smart, accessible tools that allow anyone to report emergencies and request assistance quickly. Safety and timely response are our top priorities.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="report-card">
      <h3>🤝 Our Volunteers</h3>
      <p>Our platform brings together trained volunteers, first responders, and community members who are ready to help. Every report counts, and every volunteer makes a difference.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="report-card">
      <h3>💡 Our Vision</h3>
      <p>We envision safer communities where help is always within reach. Through technology, collaboration, and awareness, we work to reduce risk and ensure timely assistance for everyone.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="report-card">
      <h3>📣 Get Involved</h3>
      <p>Join our network of volunteers, stay informed, and help us spread the word. Together, we can make a meaningful impact when disasters strike.</p>
    </div>
